com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi

Interface LucentEndpointUnregisteredEvent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AddressEvent, Event, LucentEndpointEvent

    public interface LucentEndpointUnregisteredEvent
extends LucentEndpointEvent
    This private event is used to indicate that an endpoint has unregistered from a station which was being monitored using a LucentV11AddressListener. It provides information about the endpoint.
    See Also:
    LucentV11AddressListener
